# Expo MCP

Authenticate **before** Expo-related implementation or troubleshooting:

```
CallMcpTool server=user-expo-mcp toolName=mcp_auth arguments={}
```

After auth, prefer **Expo MCP** (`search_documentation`, `read_documentation`, EAS build tools) over guessing SDK APIs or web search.

## When to query MCP

| Task | MCP topics |
|------|------------|
| Dependencies | `npx expo install`, SDK 56 version matrix |
| App config | `app.config.ts`, plugins, `expo-build-properties` |
| CNG / prebuild | `expo prebuild --clean --platform android` (Android-only) |
| EAS | `eas.json` profiles, build status, logs |
| Jest / Metro / Babel | `jest-expo`, `expo/metro-config`, `babel-preset-expo` |

## Fallback

If MCP is unavailable, use Context7 `/expo/expo` docs — not memory.

